snippet: The Nasdaq hit a 12-year closing high and the Standard & Poor’s 500 index climbed to a five-year high on stronger trade data.
abstract: Standard & Poor's 500-stock index edges to a five year high, extending a rally that began in January.
lead_paragraph: The Nasdaq hit a 12-year closing high and the Standard & Poor’s 500 index climbed to a five-year high on stronger trade data.

headline.main: S.&P. Extends Its Rally to a Five-Year High
